+## Where Humans Are Involved
+
+| Step | Who | What |
+|------|-----|------|
+| Start | Claude or human | Decide what to work on |
+| Implement | Claude | Write code |
+| Codex review | Human | Trigger review, paste results |
+| Accept/defer/reject | Claude or human | Evaluate findings |
+| Finalize | Claude | Wrap up and record |
+
+The framework intentionally does not auto-trigger Codex review. This gives the
+human control over when and how review happens.
