 ## Cycle Artifacts
 
-Each cycle directory contains:
-
 | File | Purpose |
 |------|---------|
-| `meta.json` | Cycle metadata (id, version, status, timestamps) |
-| `request.md` | What was requested for this cycle |
-| `claude-implementation-summary.md` | What Claude implemented |
-| `codex-review.md` | Codex review findings |
-| `codex-followup.md` | How review feedback was addressed |
-| `final-summary.md` | Final summary with changes and remaining items |
-| `self-application-notes.md` | Notes on how this cycle affects the framework itself |
-| `git-status.txt` | Git status snapshot |
-| `git.diff` | Git diff snapshot |
+| `meta.json` | Cycle metadata (id, version, phase, timestamps) |
+| `request.md` | What was requested (goal, context, scope) |
+| `claude-implementation-summary.md` | What was implemented (decisions, files, testing) |
+| `codex-review.md` | Review findings (High/Medium/Low severity) |
+| `codex-followup.md` | How findings were addressed (Accepted/Deferred/Rejected) |
+| `final-summary.md` | Final summary (overview, changes, remaining issues) |
+| `self-application-notes.md` | Impact on the framework's own workflow |
+| `git-status.txt` | Git status at start and finalize |
+| `git.diff` | Git diff at start and finalize |
 
